Maintainer: Satoshi Kume <satoshi.kume.1984@gmail.com>
Description: The Large Language Model (LLM) represents a groundbreaking advancement 
    in various natural language processing, and also allows us to extend the world of R. 
    Focusing on language translation and conversion in various language, 
    TransLinguaAI4R offers functionalities such as text translation, summarization, 
    text extension, and language element decomposition. 
    This package is part of the chatAI4R family.
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
